WEBVTT

00:00.532 --> 00:01.962
I want to stop doing this.

00:02.342 --> 00:04.006
<i>Previously on Mad Men...</i>

00:04.367 --> 00:07.546
It's been my privilege
to be treated like a protégé

00:07.651 --> 00:09.297
and for you to be my mentor.

00:09.451 --> 00:11.217
We're going to
lose Jaguar unless

00:11.324 --> 00:12.843
an arrangement is made...

00:12.905 --> 00:14.437
Tell them I want a partnership.

00:14.751 --> 00:16.681
My wife's a big TV star.

00:17.924 --> 00:18.919
Break a leg.

00:19.730 --> 00:20.722
<i>Beans came in today.</i>

00:20.805 --> 00:22.670
And he says he's gonna
kill the account and himself

00:22.776 --> 00:24.600
if they even talk
to ketchup again.

00:24.692 --> 00:27.522
I want you to find out
everything you can on Heinz ketchup.

